{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/CollectParams.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.mkGrindOnlyTactics\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkGrindOnlyTactics</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">cfg</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.TSyntax\">TSyntax</a> <span class=\"fn\">`Lean.Parser.Tactic.optConfig</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">seq</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.TGrind\">TGrind</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/CoreM.html#Lean.Core.CoreM\">CoreM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> (<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.TSyntax\">TSyntax</a> <span class=\"fn\">`tactic</span>))</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Given a `grind` tactic sequence, extracts parameters and builds a `grind only` tactics.\nIt returns at most two. The first tactic uses anchors to restrict the search if applicable.\nThe second does not restrict the search using anchors. The second option is included only if there\nare anchors.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/CollectParams.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.mkGrindOnlyTactics","kind":"def","line":89,"name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.mkGrindOnlyTactics","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/9d4ad1273f6cea397c3066c2c83062a4410d16bf/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/CollectParams.lean#L89-L110"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/CollectParams.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.mkFinishTactic\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkFinishTactic</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">seq</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.TGrind\">TGrind</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/CoreM.html#Lean.Core.CoreM\">CoreM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.TGrind\">TGrind</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Given a `grind` tactic sequence, extracts parameters and builds an terminal `finish only` tactic.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/CollectParams.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.mkFinishTactic","kind":"def","line":82,"name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.mkFinishTactic","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/9d4ad1273f6cea397c3066c2c83062a4410d16bf/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/CollectParams.lean#L82-L87"}}],"imports":["Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.Types"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.CollectParams"}